trans-unit.source: The DirectoryConnection class is an abstract class and cannot be instantiated.
trans-unit.target: Kan ikke startes DirectoryConnection klassen er en abstrakt klasse.

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.LdapConnection"></xref> or <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection"></xref> classes to connect to a directory server.
trans-unit.target: Bruk av <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.LdapConnection"> </xref> eller <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection"> </xref> klasser til å koble til en server.

trans-unit.source: The DirectoryConnection constructor initializes a new instance of a <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryConnection"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Konstruktøren DirectoryConnection initialiserer en ny forekomst av en <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryConnection"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: The ClientCertificates property specifies one or more client certificates to send for authentication.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen ClientCertificates angir én eller flere klientsertifikater for å sende for godkjenning.

trans-unit.source: One or more client certificates to send for authentication.
trans-unit.target: Én eller flere klientsertifikater for å sende for godkjenning.

trans-unit.source: The Credential property specifies alternate credentials for the connection object.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen legitimasjonen angir alternativ legitimasjon for tilkoblingsobjektet.

trans-unit.source: If not specified, the default value is `null`.
trans-unit.target: Hvis ikke angitt, brukes standardverdien er `null`.

trans-unit.source: Alternate credentials for the connection object.
The Directory property specifies the domain or the server to which the connection should be made.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen Directory Angir domenet eller serveren tilkoblingen skal utføres.

trans-unit.source: For example, "http://fabrikam.com/platforms/adssoap.dll" represents a DSML server and "dc-01.fabrikam.com" represents an LDAP server.
trans-unit.target: "Dc-01.fabrikam.com" representerer en LDAP-server, for eksempel "http://fabrikam.com/platforms/adssoap.dll" representerer en DSML-server.

trans-unit.source: The domain or the server to which the connection should be made.
trans-unit.target: Domenet eller serveren tilkoblingen skal utføres.

trans-unit.source: The SendRequest method sends a single directory operation to the server.
trans-unit.target: Metoden SendRequest sender en enkelt katalog-operasjon på serveren.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryRequest"></xref> object that contains the request.
A <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryResponse"></xref> object that contains the server response to the request operation.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryResponse"> </xref> objekt som inneholder serversvaret for forespørselsoperasjon.

trans-unit.source: The returned response object may be different than the requested object if the server returns a different response.
trans-unit.target: Objektet returnerte svar kan være forskjellig fra det forespurte objektet hvis serveren returnerer et annet svar.

trans-unit.source: The Timeout property contains the length of time, in seconds, before the connection times out.
trans-unit.target: Timeout-egenskapen inneholder hvor lang tid i sekunder før tilkoblingen blir tidsavbrutt.

trans-unit.source: Thirty seconds is the default time length property setting.
trans-unit.target: 30 sekunder er nå lengden egenskapen standardinnstillingen.

trans-unit.source: The length of time, in seconds, before the connection times out.
trans-unit.target: Hvor lang tid i sekunder før tilkoblingen blir tidsavbrutt.
